count.name: WA Senate 2013 - Count 1
count.description: First count of the votes, replaced by later recount.

count.name: WA Senate 2013 - Count 2
count.description: Second count of the votes. This was the result declared by the AEC.

count.name: WA Senate 2013 - Count 2 + Missing votes
count.description: Second count of the votes, plus the AEC's estimate of the 1370 votes lost during the recount. These votes were not recounted, and lost informal ballots were not re-examined, so this is very much an approximation and not conclusive as to what would have happened if the ballots had not been lost.
